<span id="freeTextContainer16179653477400261097">Hilarious. Sharp, witty writing. Not sure what else to say besides I loved it? But there&apos;s a definite Game of Thrones vibe, I think because of the warring-family aspect (ahem Lannisters) but whether you read this or see it, it&apos;s a gem.</span>
  <span id="freeText16179653477400261097" style="display:none">Hilarious. Sharp, witty writing. Not sure what else to say besides I loved it? But there's a definite Game of Thrones vibe, I think because of the warring-family aspect (ahem Lannisters) but whether you read this or see it, it's a gem.</span>
