<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer13390862710007562149">James Goldman was an American Academy Award-winning screenwriter and playwright, and the brother of screenwriter and novelist <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/12521.William_Goldman' title='William Goldman' rel='nofollow noopener'>William Goldman</a>.<br/><br/>He was born in Chicago, Illinois and grew up primarily in Highland Park, Illinois, a Chicago suburb. He is most noted as the author of <i>The Lion in Winter</i> and author of the book for the stage musical <i>Follies</i>.<br/><br/>Goldman died from a heart attack in New York City, </span>
  <span id="freeText13390862710007562149" style="display:none">James Goldman was an American Academy Award-winning screenwriter and playwright, and the brother of screenwriter and novelist <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/12521.William_Goldman" title="William Goldman" rel="nofollow noopener">William Goldman</a>.<br /><br />He was born in Chicago, Illinois and grew up primarily in Highland Park, Illinois, a Chicago suburb. He is most noted as the author of <i>The Lion in Winter</i> and author of the book for the stage musical <i>Follies</i>.<br /><br />Goldman died from a heart attack in New York City, where he had lived for many years.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13390862710007562149" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

